      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a clean look with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing some light wear on the driver's seat bolster but no rips or tears. It runs smoothly and is mechanically sound, making it a dependable choice for a buyer who wants a quality car without the premium price of a showroom-perfect example.",
