    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint still holds a nice luster, though you may find a few small stone chips on the hood and some light swirl marks from car washes. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
