    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, offered in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, resulting in a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original showroom sophistication. Beyond its aesthetic perfection, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical certification to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability. This is a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a masterfully maintained automobile that stands as a testament to automotive preservation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
